{
  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_2' aria-label=\" Narayan Das versus State of Chhattisgarh pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_289_304','2025INSC872'); ><font size='4'> <strong>NARAYAN DAS<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF CHHATTISGARH </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 8 S.C.R. 289</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 872</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010003192025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.B. PARDIWALA, R MAHADEVAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose as regards the interpretation of s.32-B of the NDPS Act by the High Court that u/s.32-B minimum punishment is considered as maximum punishment. Headnotes&dagger; Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances Act, 1985 &ndash; s.32-B &ndash; Factors to be taken into minimum punishment &ndash; High Court&rsquo;s understanding that u/s.32-B minimum punishment is considered as maximum punishment; and that at the time of imposing sentence the trial court to keep in mind the factors as provided in clauses (a) to (f) of s.32-B &ndash; Correctness: Held:<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 17-07-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CRIMINAL) No. 10310/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Dismissed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_289_304','2025INSC872','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_289_304','2025INSC872','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('2','2025','2025_8_289_304','2025INSC872');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_289_304','2025INSC872','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
